Product description

USB Charging Station for Multiple Devices USB Wall Charger 10 ports

USB Charging Station for Multiple Devices USB Wall Charger 10 ports

Multi Ports USB Charging Station:

Keep neat and tidy at home and in office with only one power cord,multi-port USB wall charger block makes you everyday happier.

High Power & High Efficiency

USB desktop charging station,wall charger has 50W and 10 usb multi-ports (5V,2.4A or 5V,1A), it can charge 10 devices simultaneously, make your life easier.

Convenient and Comfortable

This multi ports usb wall charger hub power is convenient for the whole family to charge their smartphones in airports, hotels,at home, even travelling. The input voltage of 100-240V is suitable for global and safe charging.

Broad Compatibility:

USB wall charger fit for iPhone, Samsung Galaxy, cell phones, cameras, eReaders, bluetooth speaker&headsets, power bank, MP3 /MP4 player and more. Ideal multi port USB charging station for your multiple devices.

Superior Protection:

Built-in overheat, overcharge, overcurrent, overload, short circuit protection in the USB charger block, completely ensures your devices' safety and offers them full-scale protection.

Caution

1. Keep away from heat, ammables, poisons, and corrosive substances.

2. Keep away from water, liquid, and moisture.

3. Do not drop, knock, or disassemble the charger.

4.Keep out of reach of children.

USB Charging Station has compact design

Compact & Portable Design:

Multi-port usb wall charger is lightweight and compact which is suitable for home, office, desktop even traveling. Much more space-saving and well-organized while charging.The USB charging station compact size makes the multiple usb charger hub great for travelling.

USB Charging Station for multiple devices 10 ports

This usb charging station charges up to 10 USB devices simultaneously from one wall outlet. Simply connect any USB mobile device, such as iPhone, Smartphone, a Wireless Hotspot etc. and quickly charge all your devices from one place. The USB wall charger is durable and lightweight and works great at home or in office. This is a must-have travel companion to charge all your power-hungry devices.

OVER-HEATING PROTECTION

USB charging station has over-heating protection,ensures your devices' safety and offers them full-scale protection.

OVER-VOLTAGE PROTECTION

USB wall charger has over-voltage protection,ensures your devices' safety and offers them full-scale protection.

OVER-CURRENT PROTECTION

USB charging hub power has over-current protection,ensures your devices' safety and offers them full-scale protection.

SHORT-CIRCUIT PROTECTION

USB charging block has short-circuit protection,ensures your devices' safety and offers them full-scale protection.

      My wife put this in my stocking yesterday to get us one step closer to our life goal of eliminating AA and AAA batteries from our lives (flashlings, headlamps, children's toys, etc). We have lots of ambitous life goals, but I digress. Needless to say I was very excited to recieve it since one of my kids got a USB charged RC car under the tree and I was dreading having to share my phone charger.

      So I felt a sense of urgency to get this thing plugged in to start charging all our devices. It's important to pay attention to situations that trigger this urgent feeling. This is when dangerous things happen (I'm a licensed therapist so I know).

      Despite this sense of urgency, and the fact that I already know how to use the product, I still made sure to carefully read all the instructions on the back of the box first. I'm going to provide you with the instructions so you can decide for yourself if this is a product you would like to plug into your wall. I also uploaded a picture of the instructions. Here goes:

      "Warning:
      1. Avoid the metal and water coming into the usb charger, Or'll make a fire.
      To avoid the short circuit,only work in dry environment
      2. Don't touch the charger directly when it's working as it would be a little hot.
      3. Stop using the charger when damaged
      4. Plug off when not working.
      5. Only for 12-60 year-old people."

      Well... These instructions made me confident enough to plug it right into the wall in my bedroom. Since I am between the ages of 12 and 60, I figured I could safely operate this complex machine. I threw all caution to the wind, plugged it in and attached the cord to the RC car (its always best to test these things on a child's toy first).

      There were a few sparks, the lights flickered and, yes, even a quick wiff of ozone (if you know you know), and there was a slight humming sound but in the end, the RC car was charged and the house did not burn down. In the morning we unplugged the machine on account of Warning #4: "plug off when not working".

      This hub was purchased as a main power source for a series of low-power USB grow lights I have attached to a shelving unit in my office, but it really hasn't worked as well as I would have hoped. Because of the nature of the USB grow lights, any power glitch/short automatically turns them off and they must be manually turned back on one by one. If this happened every once in a while, not a problem, but it started happening every day, and now, I can't even turn on a light without the whole hub shorting out.
      I like to think of myself as pretty tech savvy, so it's pretty frustrating to not know why this may be happening as it's connected to the same power hub as my main PC and other devices, none of which are having the same issue as this single hub. The only reason I've been able to come up with in the past 6 weeks of having it is that there's a problem in the hardware and/or it's been cheaply made. I wish I could return it, but we're past the window.
      Buyers beware!
